00:07.174 --> 00:11.545 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
On the "NewsHour" tonight: The
FBI announces
it will review a new batch of
e-mails related

00:11.578 --> 00:16.717 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
to Hillary Clinton's handling of
classified
information, while Donald
Trump's campaign

00:16.750 --> 00:18.518 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
funds dwindle.

00:18.552 --> 00:23.824 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
