sexual assault
survivors -- one woman's fight
to change the

00:23.857 --> 00:27.327 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
laws and advocate for survivors
around the
nation.

00:27.361 --> 00:31.899 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
