Founder, Rise:
Rape is notorious for being
under-reported,

00:31.932 --> 00:38.438 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
and it's because survivors are
faced with
a system that is stacked so high
against them.

00:38.472 --> 00:42.042 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
