nations, Antarctica's
Ross Sea becomes the world's
largest marine

00:48.649 --> 00:50.083 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
sanctuary.

00:50.117 --> 00:52.419 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
