stressing that it's
not clear if these e-mails are
significant.

02:32.719 --> 02:34.287 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
In Manchester, New Hampshire:

02:34.321 --> 02:35.722 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DONALD TRUMP (R), Presidential
Candidate:
That I heard this 10 minutes
ago.

02:35.756 --> 02:38.959 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
LISA DESJARDINS: The news was
certainly significant
to Donald Trump.

02:38.992 --> 02:45.866 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DONALD TRUMP: We must not let
her take her
are criminal scheme into the
Oval Office.

02:45.899 --> 02:47.734 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
(CHEERING AND APPLAUSE)

02:47.768 --> 02:55.809 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DONALD TRUMP: I have great
respect for the
fact that the FBI and the
Department of Justice

02:55.842 --> 03:04.251 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
