courage to right
the horrible mistake that they
made.

03:04.284 --> 03:09.489 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
LISA DESJARDINS: This the same
day that Clinton
hoped to focus on other areas,
like debuting

03:09.523 --> 03:11.825 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
