President Obama.

03:11.858 --> 03:13.927 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
BARACK OBAMA, President of the
United States:
These last eight years is on the
ballot.

03:13.960 --> 03:18.231 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
LISA DESJARDINS: And the Clinton
camp had
good news on the fund-raising
front, as Donald

03:18.265 --> 03:23.270 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Trump faced new money questions,
especially
about his repeated pledges to
personally finance

03:23.303 --> 03:25.672 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
his campaign, like this from two
days ago.

03:25.705 --> 03:28.542 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
DONALD TRUMP: I will have over
$100 million
in the campaign.

03:28.575 --> 03:31.344 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
And I'm prepared to go much more
than that.

03:31.378 --> 03:35.715 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
LISA DESJARDINS: But new
fund-raising reports
show the total Trump personally
donated to

03:35.749 --> 03:40.387 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
