incumbent Republican
Mark Kirk:

04:28.034 --> 04:29.870 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
SEN.

04:29.903 --> 04:32.405 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MARK KIRK (R), Illinois: I had
forgotten that
your parents came all the way
from Thailand

04:32.439 --> 04:33.840 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
