twists and
turns of campaign 2016 keep
coming.

04:48.121 --> 04:50.257 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
For the "PBS NewsHour," I'm Lisa
Desjardins.

04:50.290 --> 04:54.394 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
