school board
to accommodate the student.

05:11.077 --> 05:16.249 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The secretary of the interior
says she's -- quote
-- "profoundly disappointed"
with the acquittals

05:16.283 --> 05:19.619 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
in Oregon's wildlife refuge
takeover.

05:19.653 --> 05:24.291 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Secretary Sally Jewell says
she's concerned
that it will damage the security
and management

05:24.324 --> 05:26.126 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
of public lands.

05:26.159 --> 05:31.865 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
