vindicates their
claims of federal overreach.

05:36.002 --> 05:40.507 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
SHAWNA COX, Defendant: We have
to say we are
so grateful for the patriots and
for those

05:40.540 --> 05:43.410 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
