07:13.667 --> 07:18.471 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The rebels claim the actual
target was the
international airport at Jiddah
northwest

07:18.505 --> 07:20.307 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
of Mecca.

07:20.340 --> 07:25.245 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
