25:18.851 --> 25:24.289 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
AMANDA NGUYEN, President and
Founder, Rise:
Over and over again, I started
discovering

25:24.323 --> 25:26.458 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
is a system that is so broken.

25:26.492 --> 25:32.664 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOHN YANG: For sexual assault
survivors like
Amanda Nguyen, this small box
has the tremendous

25:32.698 --> 25:36.802 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
power to deliver justice and
bring closure.

25:36.835 --> 25:38.570 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
It's a rape kit.

25:38.604 --> 25:43.575 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Inside are the tools to collect
and store
the evidence to track down and
prosecute an

25:43.609 --> 25:45.310 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
assailant.

25:45.344 --> 25:50.449 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
AMANDA NGUYEN: Rape is notorious
for being
underreported, and it's because
survivors

25:50.482 --> 25:54.720 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
are faced with a system that is
stacked so
high against them.

25:54.753 --> 25:59.992 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOHN YANG: Amanda was assaulted
in 2013 when
she was in college in
Massachusetts.

26:00.025 --> 26:04.763 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Rape kits are automatically
destroyed in that
state after six months unless
the victim asks

26:04.797 --> 26:06.198 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
for an extension.

26:06.231 --> 26:07.966 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
And how do they do that?

26:08.000 --> 26:11.737 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
AMANDA NGUYEN: The catch is that
there's no
information given on how to
extend it, and

26:11.770 --> 26:15.040 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
the greater catch is that
there's no way to
actually extend it.

26:15.073 --> 26:20.145 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOHN YANG: Even after she filled
out the proper
forms, the bureaucratic
confusion continued.

26:20.179 --> 26:24.817 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
AMANDA NGUYEN: I found out that,
against an
extension put into place, my kit
was wrongly

26:24.850 --> 26:27.486 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
removed from the forensic lab
and almost destroyed.

26:27.519 --> 26:31.890 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
So, even if I have played by
their game, it
still is broken.

26:31.924 --> 26:35.027 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JOHN YANG: After that, Amanda
began asking
questions.

26:35.060 --> 26:39.565 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
She learned that, in most
states, police can
legally destroy rape kits well
before the

26:39.598 --> 26:41.667 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
