26:41.700 --> 26:46.338 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
AMANDA NGUYEN: What that
literally means is
that, if I was raped in a state
that doesn't

26:46.371 --> 26:53.345 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
destroy kits, like California,
Colorado, Texas,
Illinois, then this wouldn't
have happened

26:53.378 --> 26:57.549 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
to me, and it's just because
Massachusetts
doesn't have those rights.

26:57.583 --> 26:59.685 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
JOHN YANG: An activist was born.

26:59.718 --> 27:01.920 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
AMANDA NGUYEN: I had a choice.

27:01.954 --> 27:05.424 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
I could accept injustice or
rewrite the law.

27:05.457 --> 27:08.360 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And one of these things is a lot
better than
the other.

27:08.393 --> 27:12.064 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
My mission is simple: Fix the
patchwork of
rights.

27:12.097 --> 27:17.703 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOHN YANG: Amanda formed a
coalition of rape
survivors demanding a federal
bill of rights.

27:17.736 --> 27:23.141 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
A Change.org petition has more
than 140,000
signatures.

27:23.175 --> 27:28.280 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
Most sexual assaults are
investigated and
prosecuted under state law, but
Amanda believes

27:28.313 --> 27:32.784 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
that a national standard can
serve as a model
for statehouses.

27:32.818 --> 27:37.723 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Earlier this month, that finally
became a
reality when President Obama
signed the Sexual

27:37.756 --> 27:40.292 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Assault Survivors Bill of
Rights.

27:40.325 --> 27:46.098 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
It's the first time that the
term sexual assault
survivor appears in federal law.

27:46.131 --> 27:50.536 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The bill says those who've been
assaulted
should be clearly told their
legal rights,

27:50.569 --> 27:56.275 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
be able to track the status and
results of
their rape kit, not pay for a
rape kit exam,

27:56.308 --> 27:58.143 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
and be able to get the police
report.

27:58.176 --> 27:59.945 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
SEN.

