28:13.825 --> 28:15.627 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
SEN.

28:15.661 --> 28:18.931 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEANNE SHAHEEN: Oftentimes, the
