28:54.466 --> 28:59.171 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOHN YANG: Amanda's coalition is
now lobbying
state lawmakers across the
country.

28:59.204 --> 29:04.676 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
