Massachusetts.

29:08.246 --> 29:11.850 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The overall goal of the bill is
to empower
assault victims with
information.

29:11.883 --> 29:15.420 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
LINDSEY SILVERBERG, Network for
Victim Recovery
of D.C.: It's so scary, it's so
overwhelming

29:15.454 --> 29:19.925 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
