have any idea
really about what is going to
happen.

29:19.958 --> 29:25.130 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOHN YANG: MedStar Washington
Hospital Center
in the District of Columbia
offers every patient

29:25.163 --> 29:30.302 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
