forensic nurse
specially trained to conduct
those exams and

29:30.335 --> 29:34.239 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
a sexual assault advocate like
Lindsey Silverberg.

29:34.272 --> 29:37.409 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
She's there to provide victims
with legal
and emotional support.

29:37.442 --> 29:41.313 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
LINDSEY SILVERBERG: One of the
benefits of
having an advocate, with
somebody in the exam

29:41.346 --> 29:45.183 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
room and then following up after
with them,
