engage law

29:45.217 --> 29:50.389 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
enforcement after the forensic
exam is over,
they have somebody who can walk
them through

29:50.422 --> 29:52.190 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
that system.

29:52.224 --> 29:55.927 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And we have seen an increase in
the number
of people who have decided to
report to law

29:55.961 --> 30:00.465 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
enforcement after an exam, once
they have
all the information about what
that looks

30:00.499 --> 30:02.234 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
like.

30:02.267 --> 30:06.204 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOHN YANG: But, in many states,
full-time
professional advocates like
Lindsey don't

30:06.238 --> 30:08.206 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
exist.

30:08.240 --> 30:12.644 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
LINDSEY SILVERBERG: Access to
competent, well-trained
individuals, both an advocate
and a forensic

30:12.678 --> 30:15.180 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
nurse, is not the national
standard at the
moment.

30:15.213 --> 30:21.586 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOHN YANG: Amanda continues to
champion the
rights of the estimated 25
million sexual

30:21.620 --> 30:23.355 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
